  "original_title": "Pohottuwa wants Gotabaya back in Sri Lanka with security, and facilities",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Pohottuwa wants Gotabaya back in Sri Lanka with security, and facilities",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna has made a request from President Ranil Wickremesinghe to take necessary measures to bring back Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa to Sri Lanka.",
        "The SLPP also requests that Rajapaksa be awarded propoer security following his arrival and that the necessary facilities be made available.",
        "SLPP General Secretary Attorney-at-Law Sagara Kariyawasam said that the request was made during talks between the SLPP and the President today.",
        "Pohottuwa wants Gotabaya back in Sri Lanka with security, and facilities"
      ],
